HEADWORD: Sportule
<hw>Spor"tule</hw> <pr>(-t⟦umac⟧l)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sportula</ets> a little basket, a gift, dim. of <ets>sporta</ets> a
basket: cf. F. <ets>sportule</ets>.]</ety> <def>A charitable gift or
contribution; a gift; an alms; a dole; a largess; a sportula.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Ayliffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

